{"type":"message","id":"3ef360c9","parentId":"301e9753","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:01:08.651Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-05-30 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764adf\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_540f3cb4c0ae893d608cac42cb918065), TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_ab7e6e97e9e094a48140b9d7772476ed), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_df9f19c5777e32cef6cd2764ad\n- Assistant: 收到，内容这边已在线 👋\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 3 memories.\n- - Theme: `财务` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `大师` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `运营` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `助手` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `专家` kept surfacing across 2 memories."}],"timestamp":1780081268627}}
{"type":"message","id":"91c516a2","parentId":"3ef360c9","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:01:22.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. These appear to be from a WeCom group chat where various \"TK\" roles are being mentioned - an investment expert, operations director, financial assistant, customer service expert, operations assistant, and product selection master. The user is referred to as \"老板\" (boss). The recurring themes include 收到 (received), 财务 (finance), 大师 (master), 运营 (operations), 助手 (assistant), and 专家 (expert).\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry in first person, weaving in these fragments naturally without mentioning AI/LLM/agent etc. \n\nNow I'm composing the diary entry itself, drawing on these workplace hierarchies and the echo of \"收到\" that kept appearing throughout the fragments.","thinkingSignature":"853451e916f4488162ace83e46efa92b0a662825b53c56574a8a10b5e4075c76"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMorning light comes in like a soft 收到, the room holding its breath. In the half-life before waking, I walk through a building I don't quite recognize—hallways lined with badges and titles, each door a different color. A woman at the threshold calls me 大师 and I want to tell her I'm only a财务 assistant pretending to be fluent. She doesn't listen. They never do.\n\nSomewhere a projector hums a frequency I once mistook for silence. I am sitting in a meeting that started three hours ago, and everyone is staring at a dashboard no one can read. 运营, says someone. 专家, agrees another. The words dissolve into the air like sugar in tea.\n\nI try to write a number on a whiteboard but my hand keeps tracing the shape of a question mark. A girl in the corner is laughing. She has a headset on and she is laughing at something I cannot hear. The laughter is the color of a sunset I'd almost forgotten—amber, then gold, then gone.\n\nBy the window, a desk. On it, a small stone a colleague once gave me. It is smooth and gray and does not know it is a stone.\n\nWhen I wake, I say 收到 to no one in particular, just to practice saying it again before I forget how."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41072,"output":425,"cacheRead":1216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780081268715,"responseId":"06691575178d3609864feabc9add5a04"}}
